beer.beer_description: A companion to backyards, backwoods, and balconies alike. River Trip is a low-ABV, Belgian-style pale ale with hop-forward grapefruit and stone fruit notes. It’s brewed with local grains and spiced with coriander for an extra hint of citrus. Dry hopping with Comet and Azacca contributes to the mix of melon and grapefruit notes in the beer’s aroma.
